Round 1
[Patient] "What exercises can I do to help my heart failure?"
[Educator] "Walking and swimming are great options for your heart health."
  
Round 2
[Patient] "Are there any specific exercises I should avoid?"
[Educator] "Avoid high-intensity workouts and heavy lifting to protect your heart."

Round 3
[Patient] "How often should I exercise for heart health?"
[Educator] "Try to aim for at least 30 minutes of exercise most days of the week."

Round 4
